name: Car Impossible Racing Tracks 2
description:
Car Impossible Racing Tracks 2 is a proper impossible stunt car track where your are miles above the ground on the sky tracks filled with many stunts and ramps to make your experience great. Drive on these amazing tracks. Discover many real impossible tracks on your way. You are given total freedom so enjoy the fun filled game and perform flips barrels and many other stunts with your collection of beautiful cars in the garage. Dangerous track car driving have little hard and fun driving on the amazing zigzag tracks of sky ramps on road.
Features:
- Many real looking cars to drive on the tracks
- Beautiful and eye catching graphics
- Amazing tracks with dangerous sharp turns and obstacles
- All levels are thrilling and challenging which make this game more exciting car stunt game
- Fun realistic driving controls
- Dynamic camera angles to help you drive accurately.
